{"tid":1977502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑膚暴徒裝修中國工廠後 傳支那下跪會對廣州黑人派錢 每人￥5600","createTime":"2020-04-18T04:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T10:22:38.000Z","uid":54373,"like":323,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"52c0720778270274bb1f18eeeed86f0420ae9dcc","tid":1977502,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:32:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來裝修完有錢派，非洲手足站起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共歧視非裔醜聞傳全球 廣州擬補貼非裔人士5600元<br />\n廣州發生震驚全球的歧視非裔醜聞事件後，推特帳戶「冷山時評」4月17日爆料，疑有消息流出，廣州市擬給尼日利亞為主的非裔人士發放5600元生活隔離補貼。「冷山時評」指出，「我想知道，這是誰的國？」<br />\n<br />\n消息「廣州市民政局來文徵求《關於做好健康服務管理期間生活困難外籍人士在穗基本生活保障工作的實施方案》意見，擬對因受新冠肺炎疫情影響在健康服務管理期間生活困難外籍人士給予一次性生活補助（每人5600元），所需資金建議由市本級財政全額負擔。」<br />\n<br />\n儘管消息暫未到明確證實，有推特網友還是紛紛留言：<br />\n「馬列俄奸殖民中華大地啊，可悲可憐的中國人。」<br />\n<br />\n「反正不是中國人的『國』。」<br />\n<br />\n「我的下巴被驚得掉很多次了。」"},{"pid":"526d2b6687daebe22fc7919f422d18697d761967","tid":1977502,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0527e6375ac02b0c4bd92639accc512c91b69e97","tid":1977502,"uid":235875,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"出處呢?<br />\n不過開心咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1011f5ecb60d617a6c695f5d7c838ca21d81ddc0","tid":1977502,"uid":54373,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c